<div class="project-text">
    <h2 class="strong-font">The chellenge</h2>
    <p>Booking.com Hotel page is a product of over 20 years of experimentation and optimisation. With a need to meet the expectations of various hotel segments and user groups, the page has become overloaded with information. Different teams are using different approaches to grab users attention and get them into their funnel.
    We want to help users make the decision while reducing cognitive load and increasing confidence to book.  
    </p>
    <br>
    <h2 class="strong-font">The solution</h2>
    <p>Build a framework using Machine Learning to rank and display different content on the page based on user intent. 
    </p>
    <p>Build modular and scalable page layout and develop clear patterns and design guidelines for other parts of business to use.
    </p>
</div>
