    <h2 class="strong-font">The process</h2>
    <p><b>Step 01</b> - Audit of a current state and Content mapping workshop</p>
    <p><b>Step 02</b> - Identify UI and interaction patterns</p>
    <p><b>Step 03</b> - Develop basic UI rules and guidelines</p>
    <p><b>Step 03</b> - Co-design & feedback sessions to fine-tune guidelines</p>
    <p><b>Step 05</b> - Use guidelines to design the page vision</p>
    <p><b>Step 06</b> - Prepare and conduct user testing sessions</p>
    <p><b>Step 07</b> - Analyse feedback and iterate on design</p>
    <p><b>Step 08</b> - Develop the transition plan from current state towards the vision</p>
</div>

